Whoop Development Process

Created GitHub repository
`rails new Whoop`
pushed first commit to GitHub

[1] `rails new Whoop`




-----------

WHOOP DNA
a: actions
t: test
c: code
g: gedanken


# Initialize Project
  ## Setup GitHub
    [x] a: Create GitHub repository
    [x] a: Create rails project with `rails new Whoop`
    [x] c: Complete `.gitignore`

  ## Setup Gems
    [x] g: Decide what external gems to use initially
    [x] c: Update `Gemfile.rb`
    [x] a: `bundle install`

  ## Setup PostgreSQL Database
    [x] c: Complete `database.yml`
    [x] a: `rake db:create:all`

  ## Git Push
    [x] a: Push first commit to GitHub

# Initialize Models
  [x] a: `git checkout -b initialize-models`
  [x] g: Design models and db relationships
  [x] a: Generate model migrations
  [x] c: Complete model migrations
  [x] a: `rake db:migrate`
  [ ] c: Create model test skeletons for db relationships
  [ ] t: Pass all model tests
  [ ] a: Commit changes, create pull request, and merge

# Initialize Controllers
  [ ] a: `git checkout -b initialize-controllers`
  [ ] g: Design routes
  [ ] c: Complete routes
  [ ] c: Create controller test files (empty)
  [ ] a: Commit changes, create pull request, and merge

# Initialize Views
  [ ] a: `git checkout -b initialize-views`
  [ ] c: Create a blank identifying view for each route
  [ ] a: Commit changes, create pull request, and merge

# Create Database Seed
  [ ] a: `git checkout -b create-database-seed`
  [ ] c: Complete `seeds.rb`
  [ ] a: `rake db:seed`
  [ ] a: Commit changes, create pull request, and merge

% For Each Controller
  ## Create Test Spec
    [ ] a: `git checkout -b [name]-controller-spec`
    [ ] c: Create test spec
    [ ] t: Pass all controller tests
    [ ] a: Commit changes, create pull request, and merge


# Setup RSPEC
'rails generate rspec:install'

# Feature Tests

# Styling
  ## Create Style
  ## Remove Unused Views


